1
00:01:31,410 --> 00:01:34,048
=The Glamorous Night=

2
00:01:36,418 --> 00:01:38,218
(I think I'm a pretty tough woman.)

3
00:01:38,739 --> 00:01:41,498
(Because my fever broke
even before I boarded the plane.)

4
00:01:42,298 --> 00:01:44,979
(By the time I landed in Guangzhou,
I felt as strong as an ox.)

5
00:01:46,019 --> 00:01:47,778
(I told myself over and over again,)

6
00:01:48,179 --> 00:01:50,619
("Zhao Mei, you can't always
have the best of both worlds.)

7
00:01:51,138 --> 00:01:52,578
(No man is perfect.)

8
00:01:53,379 --> 00:01:55,619
(How could you not understand
such a simple truth?")

9
00:01:57,379 --> 00:01:58,539
(If I hadn't seen it,)

10
00:01:58,979 --> 00:02:01,099
(Li Dongming would still be
a perfect husband.)

11
00:02:01,698 --> 00:02:04,259
(Forget it.
I think I've convinced myself.)

12
00:02:06,594 --> 00:02:07,464
(Reacquainting)

13
00:02:07,618 --> 00:02:08,674
(Wretch)

14
00:02:08,770 --> 00:02:09,346
(Watch)

15
00:02:10,658 --> 00:02:11,464
(Slandering enemies and friends)

16
00:02:12,770 --> 00:02:14,095
(Compete)

17
00:02:14,402 --> 00:02:18,882
=Episode 11=
(Torn)

18
00:02:26,898 --> 00:02:28,458
I came straight here after landing.

19
00:02:29,779 --> 00:02:31,779
I couldn't make yesterday's flight.

20
00:02:33,298 --> 00:02:34,379
It's too packed.

21
00:02:35,698 --> 00:02:36,939
It is a bit packed.

22
00:02:37,798 --> 00:02:39,219
Excuse me, is this seat taken?

23
00:02:39,518 --> 00:02:40,018
No.

24
00:02:40,018 --> 00:02:40,659
Thank you.

25
00:02:43,298 --> 00:02:45,379
Why pick this place for training?

26
00:02:45,819 --> 00:02:47,259
There are no special places.

27
00:02:47,259 --> 00:02:48,779
And I don't like cafes.

28
00:02:48,779 --> 00:02:49,578
Here's your water.

29
00:02:49,578 --> 00:02:50,219
Thanks.

30
00:02:50,738 --> 00:02:52,018
What do cafes ever do to you?

31
00:02:52,178 --> 00:02:54,018
They haven't done anything to me.

32
00:02:54,018 --> 00:02:55,298
But this place is down-to-earth.

33
00:02:55,858 --> 00:02:58,458
Down-to-earth?
They don't even have a whiteboard.

34
00:02:59,339 --> 00:03:01,219
Look at your husband.
Why is he like this?

35
00:03:01,219 --> 00:03:03,939
I think he's too close to success
and too far from real life.

36
00:03:05,219 --> 00:03:06,578
I completely agree.

37
00:03:07,779 --> 00:03:11,138
You two seem in sync.
That puts my mind at ease.

38
00:03:12,418 --> 00:03:13,418
Good news.

39
00:03:13,659 --> 00:03:15,339
Barry said it personally

40
00:03:15,578 --> 00:03:17,178
that in a few days' executive meeting,

41
00:03:17,418 --> 00:03:18,779
he will formally

42
00:03:18,779 --> 00:03:20,738
nominate you to become

43
00:03:21,219 --> 00:03:22,779
a candidate for Sales Director.

44
00:03:24,939 --> 00:03:25,499
Really?

45
00:03:27,178 --> 00:03:28,059
He made it clear?

46
00:03:28,259 --> 00:03:30,018
Yes. He had no choice.

47
00:03:30,379 --> 00:03:31,779
Out of everyone in your company,

48
00:03:31,779 --> 00:03:34,018
you're the only woman
fit for executive promotion.

49
00:03:34,219 --> 00:03:35,379
He had no other options.

50
00:03:40,138 --> 00:03:41,738
Why do you look unhappy?

51
00:03:43,138 --> 00:03:43,738
No.

52
00:03:45,018 --> 00:03:45,979
I just didn't expect

53
00:03:45,979 --> 00:03:48,779
that my promotion
isn't because of my work ability,

54
00:03:50,339 --> 00:03:51,539
but because I'm a woman.

55
00:03:52,339 --> 00:03:53,659
It feels complicated.

56
00:03:54,738 --> 00:03:56,379
If I were you,
I wouldn't think that way.

57
00:03:56,499 --> 00:03:58,979
I'd secretly be glad I'm a woman.

58
00:03:59,458 --> 00:04:00,539
I agree with that.

59
00:04:00,659 --> 00:04:02,779
Workplace rule is
that the winner takes all.

60
00:04:03,939 --> 00:04:04,439
Alright.

61
00:04:05,499 --> 00:04:06,440
I won't overthink it.

62
00:04:06,539 --> 00:04:07,578
That's the spirit.

63
00:04:08,499 --> 00:04:08,999
This

64
00:04:11,659 --> 00:04:12,458
is for you.

65
00:04:12,458 --> 00:04:15,539
(ROLEX)

66
00:04:15,539 --> 00:04:16,039
Waiter.

67
00:04:16,459 --> 00:04:16,959
Hello.

68
00:04:20,459 --> 00:04:20,979
What's this?

69
00:04:21,938 --> 00:04:22,779
It's a blessing.

70
00:04:23,258 --> 00:04:25,818
More accurately,
it's in advance of wishing you

71
00:04:26,219 --> 00:04:27,418
unstoppable success.

72
00:04:31,539 --> 00:04:33,738
Why did you suddenly think
to give me a watch?

73
00:04:34,219 --> 00:04:36,139
I felt it suited you better
than other jewelry.

74
00:04:36,738 --> 00:04:39,459
Necklaces and rings
emphasize femininity too much.

75
00:04:40,258 --> 00:04:41,699
At your current level,

76
00:04:42,058 --> 00:04:44,139
it's a fierce battle
with no regard for gender.

77
00:04:44,659 --> 00:04:46,779
You will face indiscriminate attacks.

78
00:04:47,378 --> 00:04:50,258
No one will hold back against you
because you're a woman.

79
00:04:50,618 --> 00:04:51,298
A watch

80
00:04:51,979 --> 00:04:54,459
symbolizes control over time

81
00:04:55,058 --> 00:04:56,298
and power.

82
00:04:56,938 --> 00:04:58,378
It suits who you are now better.

83
00:04:59,659 --> 00:05:02,258
It also carries my expectations for you.

84
00:05:04,539 --> 00:05:05,099
You like it?

85
00:05:07,779 --> 00:05:08,498
I do.

86
00:05:09,938 --> 00:05:10,498
Thank you.

87
00:05:10,818 --> 00:05:13,498
Alright, stop showing off
your affection.

88
00:05:13,779 --> 00:05:14,738
Someone's preening.

89
00:05:16,738 --> 00:05:18,659
A husband like yours is hard to come by.

90
00:05:18,779 --> 00:05:21,219
You know, all the male partners
at our firm

91
00:05:21,459 --> 00:05:22,818
each want their wives

92
00:05:22,818 --> 00:05:24,539
to stay at home and care for the family.

93
00:05:24,539 --> 00:05:25,738
But him?

94
00:05:25,738 --> 00:05:29,378
He's the only one
pushing his wife to climb higher.

95
00:05:30,498 --> 00:05:31,498
Why not thank me?

96
00:05:31,899 --> 00:05:34,699
Thanks shouldn't just be spoken.

97
00:05:36,258 --> 00:05:37,618
For that project you want to do,

98
00:05:38,378 --> 00:05:39,579
I'll vote yes.

99
00:05:41,498 --> 00:05:42,498
Thank you so much.

100
00:05:43,058 --> 00:05:44,659
Consider Zhao Mei's matter settled.

101
00:05:51,058 --> 00:05:51,938
I'm buying cigarettes.

102
00:05:52,539 --> 00:05:53,219
I'll go.

103
00:05:53,498 --> 00:05:53,998
No need.

104
00:05:55,498 --> 00:05:56,699
Smoking again?

105
00:05:58,818 --> 00:05:59,579
(I can't.)

106
00:06:00,539 --> 00:06:01,699
(I overestimated myself.)

107
00:06:03,298 --> 00:06:05,579
(When Li Dongming
appeared in front of me,)

108
00:06:06,579 --> 00:06:08,136
(my stomach started churning again.)

109
00:06:09,699 --> 00:06:11,339
(When he took out that watch)

110
00:06:11,659 --> 00:06:14,498
(and made those comments
about genderless battle,)

111
00:06:15,498 --> 00:06:19,099
(I just wanted to tell him,
"You're utterly despicable.")

112
00:06:20,339 --> 00:06:21,219
(Obviously,)

113
00:06:22,339 --> 00:06:24,808
(I'll never achieve greatness.
I'm not cut out for it.)

114
00:06:26,088 --> 00:06:27,139
(I need to divorce.)

115
00:06:46,899 --> 00:06:47,399
Ms. Qiao.

116
00:06:47,938 --> 00:06:49,099
(FY Express)
I was about to bring these up to you.

117
00:06:49,298 --> 00:06:49,798
Here.

118
00:06:50,378 --> 00:06:51,178
These are?

119
00:06:51,738 --> 00:06:52,899
Chestnuts from my hometown.

120
00:06:53,019 --> 00:06:54,418
I saw your post on Moments.

121
00:06:54,539 --> 00:06:55,738
I knew you loved chestnuts.

122
00:06:55,858 --> 00:06:57,058
Mine are rare in Guangzhou.

123
00:06:57,339 --> 00:06:58,178
If you enjoy them,

124
00:06:58,178 --> 00:06:59,258
I'll have more sent to you.

125
00:07:00,539 --> 00:07:01,539
No need for formalities.

126
00:07:02,738 --> 00:07:05,418
It's not formality.
You always give me good reviews.

127
00:07:05,738 --> 00:07:07,178
I wanted to thank you.

128
00:07:07,659 --> 00:07:08,498
They're inexpensive.

129
00:07:09,219 --> 00:07:09,899
Not at all.

130
00:07:10,099 --> 00:07:11,418
I'll place them here for you.

131
00:07:14,058 --> 00:07:14,699
Okay.

132
00:07:15,899 --> 00:07:16,899
Thanks.

133
00:07:16,899 --> 00:07:17,418
Sure.

134
00:07:22,818 --> 00:07:24,498
Can you do it? Need a hand?

135
00:07:24,858 --> 00:07:25,498
I'm fine.

136
00:07:25,498 --> 00:07:26,139
Thanks.

137
00:08:11,938 --> 00:08:12,459
Tao?

138
00:08:37,858 --> 00:08:39,099
Exhausted.

139
00:08:53,058 --> 00:09:00,040
(Wretch)

140
00:09:17,666 --> 00:09:23,714
(Ultra-thin)

141
00:09:29,538 --> 00:09:31,618
Tao Ling! Tao Ling!

142
00:09:34,658 --> 00:09:35,939
Tao Ling, I know you hate me.

143
00:09:36,538 --> 00:09:38,538
But targeting me with insults?
What's the point?

144
00:09:38,738 --> 00:09:40,518
Ruijin has so many partners and CEOs.

145
00:09:41,018 --> 00:09:42,459
If you're so capable, go after them.

146
00:09:42,538 --> 00:09:43,738
You don't dare.

147
00:09:43,738 --> 00:09:45,378
You still want to work in consulting.

148
00:09:45,378 --> 00:09:46,858
You won't risk offending anyone.

149
00:09:46,858 --> 00:09:48,099
Listen to me, Tao Ling.

150
00:09:48,738 --> 00:09:50,579
I'm not a pushover.

151
00:09:50,738 --> 00:09:53,658
If you dare spread rumors
about me again,

152
00:09:54,219 --> 00:09:54,898
I promise

153
00:09:55,658 --> 00:09:57,018
I'll do everything in my power

154
00:09:57,378 --> 00:09:58,778
to ensure you're forever jobless.

155
00:09:58,939 --> 00:10:01,419
Whenever I learn where you apply,

156
00:10:01,858 --> 00:10:03,618
I'll call that company's HR.

157
00:10:03,618 --> 00:10:04,378
I'll tell them

158
00:10:04,858 --> 00:10:07,138
you were fired for poor performance

159
00:10:07,299 --> 00:10:08,538
and bad character.

160
00:10:09,258 --> 00:10:10,979
I'll make sure you never find a job.

161
00:10:10,979 --> 00:10:13,339
You're useless! You're a wretch!

162
00:10:23,498 --> 00:10:24,219
Ms. Zhao,

163
00:10:24,819 --> 00:10:25,738
to be honest,

164
00:10:25,858 --> 00:10:29,538
your speech video went viral
in our law firm's group.

165
00:10:30,699 --> 00:10:31,579
I wondered

166
00:10:31,738 --> 00:10:34,699
if your husband
was upset about your words.

167
00:10:36,099 --> 00:10:37,059
Not exactly.

168
00:10:37,498 --> 00:10:39,898
He admired my actions
and thought I was brave,

169
00:10:40,099 --> 00:10:40,898
full of strength.

170
00:10:42,378 --> 00:10:44,378
Then he turned around and cheated.

171
00:10:47,459 --> 00:10:47,959
Okay.

172
00:10:48,618 --> 00:10:50,819
But since it's a divorce case,

173
00:10:50,898 --> 00:10:52,138
it involves a lot of privacy.

174
00:10:52,618 --> 00:10:55,059
So I personally recommend
a female lawyer.

175
00:10:55,579 --> 00:10:57,459
Our firm
has many excellent female lawyers.

176
00:10:57,898 --> 00:10:59,419
Would you like me to recommend one?

177
00:10:59,979 --> 00:11:00,538
No need.

178
00:11:02,699 --> 00:11:04,618
I believe you'll win the case for me.

179
00:11:05,658 --> 00:11:06,339
And

180
00:11:07,618 --> 00:11:08,979
you'll secure a dignified victory.

181
00:11:10,819 --> 00:11:13,378
What do you mean by that?

182
00:11:14,858 --> 00:11:15,858
Leaving him some room.

183
00:11:17,618 --> 00:11:19,378
I don't quite understand that.

184
00:11:20,138 --> 00:11:21,459
You're getting divorced.

185
00:11:21,979 --> 00:11:25,219
Why spare your husband's feelings
or give him leeway?

186
00:11:27,099 --> 00:11:28,618
He's close with our top boss

187
00:11:28,618 --> 00:11:30,579
and has deep ties
with many of my colleagues.

188
00:11:31,018 --> 00:11:32,898
Lately, I've been pursuing a promotion.

189
00:11:33,498 --> 00:11:34,819
If things get too nasty,

190
00:11:35,699 --> 00:11:36,858
it'll reflect poorly on me.

191
00:11:39,939 --> 00:11:40,579
Understood.

192
00:11:41,459 --> 00:11:43,579
Any other requests then?

193
00:11:44,459 --> 00:11:46,819
My ideal outcome is
that this divorce achieves as follows.

194
00:11:47,898 --> 00:11:48,398
First,

195
00:11:49,778 --> 00:11:50,618
I get my vengeance.

196
00:11:52,419 --> 00:11:52,919
Second,

197
00:11:53,898 --> 00:11:54,898
he doesn't hate me much.

198
00:11:56,738 --> 00:11:57,979
(If he values his reputation,)

199
00:11:58,219 --> 00:12:00,898
(then this photo can
become our leverage.)

200
00:12:02,059 --> 00:12:05,378
(From now on, find a way to uncover)

201
00:12:05,378 --> 00:12:06,738
(your husband's income.)

202
00:12:07,016 --> 00:12:09,646
(Before figuring out his assets,)

203
00:12:10,184 --> 00:12:11,368
(don't make any rash moves.)

204
00:12:11,752 --> 00:12:14,699
(Don't let him sense
you're considering divorce.)

205
00:12:26,498 --> 00:12:26,998
Small world.

206
00:12:29,579 --> 00:12:30,179
Yeah.

207
00:12:33,579 --> 00:12:35,304
I didn't expect you
to be a morning runner.

208
00:12:38,699 --> 00:12:40,179
Mostly, I prefer running at night.

209
00:12:40,538 --> 00:12:42,138
I started
enjoying morning runs recently.

210
00:12:47,498 --> 00:12:48,819
You told Zeng Zixuan

211
00:12:49,579 --> 00:12:52,099
your favorite thing
about the company is the high pay?

212
00:12:52,099 --> 00:12:53,459
She even told you that?

213
00:12:55,498 --> 00:12:57,339
It's in her interview report.

214
00:12:58,018 --> 00:13:00,699
The report
is for HR and department heads.

215
00:13:01,138 --> 00:13:01,858
You didn't know?

216
00:13:04,219 --> 00:13:06,378
I didn't expect it,
but I meant what I said.

217
00:13:07,579 --> 00:13:09,219
But the offer GST gave me

218
00:13:09,219 --> 00:13:11,592
is indeed 30 percent higher
than those of similar companies.

219
00:13:12,618 --> 00:13:14,138
That's your Sales Department.

220
00:13:14,498 --> 00:13:17,138
Promoters only make
a few thousand a month.

221
00:13:17,378 --> 00:13:19,219
And you said the company pays well?

222
00:13:25,459 --> 00:13:26,018
I was wrong.

223
00:13:36,618 --> 00:13:37,778
Ms. Zhao, Mr. Dong.

224
00:13:40,018 --> 00:13:40,518
Hello.

225
00:13:41,099 --> 00:13:41,658
24th floor.

226
00:13:42,219 --> 00:13:42,719
Okay.

227
00:13:44,358 --> 00:13:44,858
Here.

228
00:13:44,858 --> 00:13:46,459
Is 3 PM today okay?

229
00:13:46,579 --> 00:13:47,079
Yes.

230
00:13:48,299 --> 00:13:48,819
Alright.

231
00:13:49,979 --> 00:13:50,819
(You're right.)

232
00:13:51,138 --> 00:13:52,618
We can't audit Zhao Mei specifically.

233
00:13:53,219 --> 00:13:54,979
Xu Yuntian already has issues.

234
00:13:55,219 --> 00:13:57,258
If Zhao Mei has issues too,
what about others?

235
00:13:58,179 --> 00:14:00,699
Does that mean
the entire GST Sales Dept. has problems?

236
00:14:02,339 --> 00:14:05,059
The VIP client dinner
is happening very soon.

237
00:14:05,219 --> 00:14:07,738
We absolutely cannot audit
at this critical moment.

238
00:14:08,339 --> 00:14:09,299
We'd be a joke.

239
00:14:09,858 --> 00:14:12,219
Mr. Shen is overstepping his bounds.

240
00:14:12,219 --> 00:14:14,738
Now that I know about this,
I'll talk to him.

241
00:14:15,018 --> 00:14:16,699
But Mr. Shen's concerns are valid.

242
00:14:17,018 --> 00:14:19,819
If Barry really pushes
female empowerment

243
00:14:19,979 --> 00:14:22,738
regardless of reality,
it would be troublesome.

244
00:14:23,099 --> 00:14:24,138
I actually have an idea.

245
00:14:24,979 --> 00:14:26,858
Isn't Zhao Mei aiming
to be the Sales Director?

246
00:14:27,099 --> 00:14:29,219
Since she's in sales,
she has to meet targets.

247
00:14:30,138 --> 00:14:32,018
The KPIs for Q4 are so demanding.

248
00:14:32,618 --> 00:14:33,579
Have her share them.

249
00:14:34,618 --> 00:14:35,939
That's a good idea.

250
00:14:36,378 --> 00:14:38,219
She wants to showcase
female strength, right?

251
00:14:38,979 --> 00:14:40,138
Let her showcase it.

252
00:14:41,138 --> 00:14:42,699
Speaking of the VIP dinner,

253
00:14:42,699 --> 00:14:46,258
the company decided you, Zhao Mei,
and Tang Lide will co-lead it.

254
00:14:46,898 --> 00:14:49,738
But when I asked Mr. Shen last night,
he said he couldn't attend.

255
00:14:49,858 --> 00:14:50,858
What's going on?

256
00:14:51,898 --> 00:14:53,099
It might be because

257
00:14:54,378 --> 00:14:55,538
Shen Xing and I broke up.

258
00:14:55,939 --> 00:14:56,439
What?

259
00:14:57,819 --> 00:14:58,339
Why?

260
00:15:04,099 --> 00:15:05,898
Sorry, that's your privacy.

261
00:15:06,378 --> 00:15:09,059
But I suggest
not making this public yet.

262
00:15:10,099 --> 00:15:12,579
Although Barry leans towards Zhao Mei,

263
00:15:12,858 --> 00:15:15,738
nothing's certain until it's finalized.

264
00:15:17,299 --> 00:15:19,059
Regardless of your relationship
with Shen Mo,

265
00:15:19,059 --> 00:15:21,179
I support you. Understand?

266
00:15:21,459 --> 00:15:21,959
Understood.

267
00:15:22,378 --> 00:15:24,819
But Mr. Shen must attend the VIP dinner.

268
00:15:25,219 --> 00:15:27,138
He's our biggest distributor, after all.

269
00:15:29,099 --> 00:15:30,979
Maybe have Liang Danning invite him?

270
00:15:31,179 --> 00:15:33,059
I heard Mr. Shen likes her.

271
00:15:33,618 --> 00:15:34,819
And it's a bit... you know.

272
00:15:35,618 --> 00:15:36,819
Better not send Liang Danning.

273
00:15:36,819 --> 00:15:39,258
I heard she's divorcing her husband.

274
00:15:41,858 --> 00:15:43,339
Well, I see.

275
00:15:50,858 --> 00:15:51,358
Here.

276
00:15:52,778 --> 00:15:53,819
The roast goose is here.

277
00:15:55,018 --> 00:15:55,579
Everyone,

278
00:15:56,099 --> 00:15:59,299
can a 1973 wine still have tannins?

279
00:15:59,658 --> 00:16:00,158
Boss.

280
00:16:00,618 --> 00:16:01,498
- Boss.
- Boss.

281
00:16:08,898 --> 00:16:10,939
This VIP dinner is
our department's first appearance

282
00:16:10,939 --> 00:16:13,099
in front of clients since Mr. Xu left.

283
00:16:13,658 --> 00:16:16,658
So I need you all to give it all

284
00:16:16,979 --> 00:16:18,099
and invite maximum clients.

285
00:16:19,219 --> 00:16:20,538
What's the higher-ups thinking?

286
00:16:21,179 --> 00:16:22,939
It's our event.

287
00:16:23,299 --> 00:16:24,744
Why involve Promotions Department?

288
00:16:25,018 --> 00:16:25,979
Why co-host with them?

289
00:16:26,258 --> 00:16:27,378
Isn't it obvious?

290
00:16:27,658 --> 00:16:30,219
The higher-ups want to boost
Promotions Department.

291
00:16:31,018 --> 00:16:31,858
That's ridiculous.

292
00:16:34,699 --> 00:16:35,258
What's wrong?

293
00:16:42,819 --> 00:16:45,658
Whatever you're thinking,
keep it to yourselves.

294
00:16:46,898 --> 00:16:48,579
With clients, I have one demand,

295
00:16:50,219 --> 00:16:50,738
unity.

296
00:16:52,579 --> 00:16:53,079
Boss.

297
00:16:53,158 --> 00:16:53,658
Unity.

298
00:16:53,658 --> 00:16:54,538
We're very united.

299
00:16:54,538 --> 00:16:55,038
Yes.

300
00:16:56,099 --> 00:16:58,018
Besides the VIP dinner,
today I also want

301
00:17:00,059 --> 00:17:01,419
to discuss the KPIs.

302
00:17:04,578 --> 00:17:06,619
Some had decent Q3 performance,

303
00:17:06,899 --> 00:17:08,179
but slacked off in Q4.

304
00:17:09,058 --> 00:17:09,558
Why?

305
00:17:11,778 --> 00:17:12,818
Did clients quit drinking?

306
00:17:14,899 --> 00:17:18,578
Or did you front-load all the Q4 stock

307
00:17:19,098 --> 00:17:19,699
in Q3?

308
00:17:22,119 --> 00:17:24,578
(Seriously, you can just say my name.)

309
00:17:29,219 --> 00:17:30,258
I don't care

310
00:17:31,578 --> 00:17:33,058
what the reason is for now.

311
00:17:33,058 --> 00:17:34,578
But I expect you to know

312
00:17:36,459 --> 00:17:37,419
where you stand.

313
00:17:37,859 --> 00:17:39,578
(I knew he wouldn't
let my private meeting)

314
00:17:39,578 --> 00:17:41,018
(with Shen Mo slide.)

315
00:17:44,179 --> 00:17:44,679
Eat.

316
00:17:46,818 --> 00:17:47,939
Let's eat. I'm starving.

317
00:17:49,738 --> 00:17:51,058
Waiter, please open the wine.

318
00:17:51,578 --> 00:17:53,699
(No, I need to prove my loyalty).

319
00:17:54,338 --> 00:17:55,659
(A wise man knows when to yield.)

320
00:17:59,010 --> 00:18:00,939
(The Genuieness Cantonese Restaurant)

321
00:18:00,939 --> 00:18:01,979
We can't tailor the liquor

322
00:18:01,979 --> 00:18:03,498
for each client at the VIP dinner,

323
00:18:03,578 --> 00:18:05,659
but we can aim
to please the overall palate.

324
00:18:06,298 --> 00:18:06,798
Boss,

325
00:18:08,419 --> 00:18:10,338
I'd like to have a word
with you privately.

326
00:18:11,699 --> 00:18:12,338
You go ahead.

327
00:18:18,139 --> 00:18:18,659
Boss,

328
00:18:19,939 --> 00:18:21,859
I understood what you just said.

329
00:18:22,098 --> 00:18:23,899
Indeed, I didn't start Q4 off well.

330
00:18:24,179 --> 00:18:26,139
But rest assured,
I'll work hard to catch up.

331
00:18:30,058 --> 00:18:32,179
You're responsible
for the VIP channel. So...

332
00:18:33,498 --> 00:18:35,258
Add extra effort
to the Nansha VIP dinner.

333
00:18:37,538 --> 00:18:38,419
I definitely will.

334
00:18:38,979 --> 00:18:42,058
I'll organize the client list right away
and get in touch with them.

335
00:18:44,018 --> 00:18:44,518
I'm off.

336
00:18:46,939 --> 00:18:47,699
Thanks, boss.

337
00:18:57,098 --> 00:18:57,598
Peter Du?

338
00:18:58,558 --> 00:18:59,558
No,

339
00:18:59,659 --> 00:19:00,459
I mean...

340
00:19:00,498 --> 00:19:01,979
Yes, Boss Peter.

341
00:19:02,538 --> 00:19:04,058
Are you still at the office?

342
00:19:04,514 --> 00:19:09,233
(Gustav Sapet China)

343
00:19:19,058 --> 00:19:20,659
Hello, I need to see Mr. Peter.

344
00:19:24,578 --> 00:19:26,899
Hello, I need to see Mr. Peter.

345
00:19:27,818 --> 00:19:28,776
Names are on the doors.

346
00:19:33,179 --> 00:19:33,699
Thanks.

347
00:19:43,338 --> 00:19:44,619
Hello, this door won't open.

348
00:19:44,979 --> 00:19:46,139
It's 15-second access.

349
00:19:47,219 --> 00:19:47,719
Get in.

350
00:19:57,298 --> 00:19:59,979
(You mean for me to invite Shen Mo?)

351
00:20:01,659 --> 00:20:03,818
But Shen Mo is Dong Yue's client.

352
00:20:04,459 --> 00:20:08,058
I know, but clearly
Dong Yue couldn't get him to come.

353
00:20:08,979 --> 00:20:10,818
And our VIP dinner

354
00:20:11,338 --> 00:20:12,979
absolutely cannot be without Shen Mo.

355
00:20:13,538 --> 00:20:15,419
So it's up to you to find a way.

356
00:20:17,498 --> 00:20:20,379
I know Shen Mo thinks highly of you.

357
00:20:21,018 --> 00:20:23,139
He even referred several deals to you.

358
00:20:23,699 --> 00:20:24,619
That's...

359
00:20:24,619 --> 00:20:26,498
He told me that himself.

360
00:20:28,338 --> 00:20:30,619
Shen Mo is our biggest distributor.

361
00:20:31,139 --> 00:20:34,139
Even Barry is very wary of him.

362
00:20:35,419 --> 00:20:38,139
Since you've made a good start with him.

363
00:20:38,979 --> 00:20:40,699
I mean the start
of a working relationship.

364
00:20:41,338 --> 00:20:42,818
Then just keep it up.

365
00:20:44,139 --> 00:20:45,859
It isn't just good for the company.

366
00:20:45,859 --> 00:20:47,219
It's good for you too.

367
00:20:47,538 --> 00:20:49,578
If Shen Mo becomes your client,

368
00:20:49,979 --> 00:20:52,619
your position in the Sales Department
will be unquestionable.

369
00:20:54,298 --> 00:20:56,338
All I can say is I'll try.

370
00:20:56,659 --> 00:20:57,899
But I can't guarantee anything.

371
00:20:58,659 --> 00:21:00,859
No guarantee needed. Just do your best.

372
00:21:14,498 --> 00:21:19,042
(Shen Mo: Mr. Shen, you...)

373
00:21:34,818 --> 00:21:35,379
Mom?

374
00:21:39,538 --> 00:21:40,939
Hadn't I come back in time,

375
00:21:41,379 --> 00:21:43,338
you'd have emptied my place.

376
00:21:43,899 --> 00:21:45,699
Mom, I didn't steal money.

377
00:21:45,699 --> 00:21:46,498
I was taking...

378
00:21:46,498 --> 00:21:47,578
- Taking what?
- I was taking...

379
00:21:47,578 --> 00:21:48,219
My wife's money.

380
00:21:48,219 --> 00:21:49,538
That's stealing, gambling addict.

381
00:21:49,659 --> 00:21:51,018
What's wrong with taking her money?

382
00:21:51,018 --> 00:21:52,179
You've ruined my daughter.

383
00:21:52,179 --> 00:21:53,498
Let's talk calmly.

384
00:21:53,699 --> 00:21:54,379
- Mom.
- Don't call me Mom!

385
00:21:54,379 --> 00:21:55,298
Let's talk calmly.

386
00:21:55,298 --> 00:21:56,119
Don't call me Mom!

387
00:21:56,119 --> 00:21:57,018
- Calm down.
- Stop!

388
00:21:57,018 --> 00:21:57,518
Mom!

389
00:21:57,538 --> 00:21:58,818
Get back here!

390
00:21:58,939 --> 00:22:00,058
Mom, Mom, don't!

391
00:22:00,098 --> 00:22:00,859
I'll kill you!

392
00:22:01,258 --> 00:22:02,778
- Mom, calm down.
- You stole money!

393
00:22:02,778 --> 00:22:04,018
- Mom!
- You stole things!

394
00:22:04,018 --> 00:22:04,818
Stop!

395
00:22:05,058 --> 00:22:06,699
I'll break your legs!

396
00:22:06,939 --> 00:22:07,859
Stop right there!

397
00:22:08,538 --> 00:22:09,818
Mom, Mom, stay calm.

398
00:22:09,979 --> 00:22:10,578
Mom,

399
00:22:10,578 --> 00:22:11,498
you can't do this.

400
00:22:11,738 --> 00:22:13,219
It'll be a criminal crime.

401
00:22:13,219 --> 00:22:14,098
Just try running!

402
00:22:14,258 --> 00:22:14,979
Take this!

403
00:22:14,979 --> 00:22:15,619
Mom, Mom.

404
00:22:15,619 --> 00:22:16,258
I'll kill you!

405
00:22:16,258 --> 00:22:17,818
It'll be a criminal crime.

406
00:22:17,818 --> 00:22:18,859
- Mom.
- Don't you dare run!

407
00:22:18,859 --> 00:22:19,538
- Mom.
- Mom! Calm down.

408
00:22:19,538 --> 00:22:20,498
I'll kill you!

409
00:22:21,159 --> 00:22:21,659
Mom.

410
00:22:21,659 --> 00:22:22,578
Stop!

411
00:22:22,578 --> 00:22:23,078
Mom!

412
00:22:23,298 --> 00:22:24,578
Mom, calm down.

413
00:22:24,578 --> 00:22:25,899
You have a heart condition, Mom.

414
00:22:25,899 --> 00:22:27,659
Run? Now take this!

415
00:22:27,659 --> 00:22:29,338
Yao Xiaohui, run!

416
00:22:30,018 --> 00:22:30,619
Run?

417
00:22:30,619 --> 00:22:31,139
Stop!

418
00:22:31,139 --> 00:22:32,379
So many people are watching.

419
00:22:32,379 --> 00:22:33,258
- Run?
- Don't make a scene.

420
00:22:33,258 --> 00:22:34,219
Go! Leave!

421
00:22:34,399 --> 00:22:34,899
Mom.

422
00:22:34,899 --> 00:22:35,699
Stop right there!

423
00:22:36,098 --> 00:22:37,098
He's Weiwei's father.

424
00:22:37,098 --> 00:22:38,619
Can you save face for Weiwei, Mom?

425
00:22:39,578 --> 00:22:40,578
Stop!

426
00:22:40,578 --> 00:22:42,338
Go! Just go!

427
00:22:42,659 --> 00:22:43,179
Mom.

428
00:22:43,459 --> 00:22:45,018
Mom.

429
00:22:45,338 --> 00:22:46,338
He's Weiwei's father.

430
00:22:46,818 --> 00:22:48,818
Let's go home and not talk here.

431
00:22:49,258 --> 00:22:49,859
Take the knife.

432
00:22:50,139 --> 00:22:51,018
Take the knife back.

433
00:22:54,298 --> 00:22:55,939
The shop needs me. I'm going back.

434
00:22:57,738 --> 00:22:59,498
Ms. Liang, don't get so worked up.

435
00:22:59,498 --> 00:23:01,018
It's fine.

436
00:23:01,379 --> 00:23:02,139
It's fine.

437
00:23:02,578 --> 00:23:04,379
Come and sit at my shop.

438
00:23:05,219 --> 00:23:05,939
Let's go.

439
00:23:06,859 --> 00:23:07,738
Let's go.

440
00:23:15,338 --> 00:23:16,018
Mr. Shen.

441
00:23:18,018 --> 00:23:19,058
- Mr. Jin, hello.
- Hello.

442
00:23:19,058 --> 00:23:20,258
What are you doing here?

443
00:23:20,379 --> 00:23:21,818
We just finished playing golf.

444
00:23:22,139 --> 00:23:24,738
Mr. Shen said
there's a great hot pot place nearby

445
00:23:24,738 --> 00:23:26,738
that tastes amazing.
So he brought me to try it.

446
00:23:27,018 --> 00:23:29,139
Yeah, you took me there once before.

447
00:23:29,419 --> 00:23:30,659
I forgot the address.

448
00:23:32,018 --> 00:23:34,098
Actually, this hot pot place
is really close. It's...

449
00:23:36,538 --> 00:23:37,379
I'll take you there.

450
00:23:37,778 --> 00:23:38,278
Great.

451
00:23:38,459 --> 00:23:39,379
Wait a second.

452
00:23:44,219 --> 00:23:45,619
My eyes are a bit irritated.

453
00:23:46,498 --> 00:23:47,219
Sorry.

454
00:23:50,338 --> 00:23:51,018
Okay, let's go.

455
00:23:53,090 --> 00:23:55,720
(Lao You Eatery)

456
00:23:55,939 --> 00:23:57,018
Thank you.

457
00:23:57,899 --> 00:23:58,498
Ms. Liang.

458
00:23:59,498 --> 00:24:00,619
The flavor of this place

459
00:24:00,619 --> 00:24:02,298
is truly exceptional.

460
00:24:02,899 --> 00:24:04,179
Especially this dipping sauce.

461
00:24:05,098 --> 00:24:07,018
It's so unique.

462
00:24:07,018 --> 00:24:09,859
It's the owner's secret recipe.
Nowhere else to be found.

463
00:24:11,738 --> 00:24:13,778
Last time you said
you'd take me for flower crabs.

464
00:24:14,338 --> 00:24:14,979
When will we go?

465
00:24:15,338 --> 00:24:17,738
Anytime. How about tonight then?

466
00:24:17,738 --> 00:24:19,498
How about
some late-night snacks tonight?

467
00:24:19,738 --> 00:24:21,098
Not tonight.

468
00:24:21,338 --> 00:24:23,219
We just ate so much.
How could we eat more?

469
00:24:23,619 --> 00:24:25,058
I'll find you another day.

470
00:24:25,058 --> 00:24:26,018
Okay, another day.

471
00:24:26,619 --> 00:24:28,578
By the way, Mr. Shen, Mr. Jin.

472
00:24:29,058 --> 00:24:31,538
Our company is hosting a VIP dinner
at Nansha Garden,

473
00:24:31,578 --> 00:24:33,139
specifically for our VIP clients.

474
00:24:33,338 --> 00:24:35,419
I believe the invitations
are sent to you.

475
00:24:36,018 --> 00:24:37,619
If you're free, come join us.

476
00:24:38,098 --> 00:24:39,578
The scenery in Nansha is...

477
00:24:40,419 --> 00:24:43,859
And the chef's cooking
is especially delicious. How about it?

478
00:24:45,338 --> 00:24:48,219
I already told your boss
I have plans this weekend.

479
00:24:50,659 --> 00:24:51,818
What about you, Mr. Jin?

480
00:24:52,419 --> 00:24:54,179
Sorry, I happen to be busy that day too.

481
00:24:56,578 --> 00:24:57,979
That's a real pity.

482
00:25:07,338 --> 00:25:08,818
Put the liquor here. Over here.

483
00:25:09,098 --> 00:25:10,979
Make sure
you note the 25-year-old ones clearly.

484
00:25:11,419 --> 00:25:12,979
Note the quantity. Handle with care.

485
00:25:13,578 --> 00:25:14,219
Secure it well.

486
00:25:14,818 --> 00:25:16,498
Mr. Li. Mr. Li.

487
00:25:17,578 --> 00:25:19,139
Drive slowly later.

488
00:25:19,479 --> 00:25:19,979
(Shen Xing: I declare I sever ties)
Drive slowly.

489
00:25:19,979 --> 00:25:21,379
(with Shen Mo as father and daughter.)
Slow over the bumps, okay?

490
00:25:21,379 --> 00:25:22,298
It's a lot of liquor.

491
00:25:23,058 --> 00:25:23,619
Thanks.

492
00:25:23,619 --> 00:25:24,818
Morning, Dong.

493
00:25:25,538 --> 00:25:26,038
Tang.

494
00:25:31,578 --> 00:25:32,338
What are you doing?

495
00:25:33,379 --> 00:25:34,459
Nothing. Checking Moments.

496
00:25:36,738 --> 00:25:37,659
I've taken

497
00:25:37,659 --> 00:25:39,899
to scrolling for short jokes
in the group.

498
00:25:41,419 --> 00:25:42,459
Other stuff annoys me.

499
00:25:42,979 --> 00:25:45,778
Jokes make me laugh.
Simple pleasures for the poor.

500
00:25:46,219 --> 00:25:47,778
What? You are poor?

501
00:25:47,899 --> 00:25:48,818
How am I not poor?

502
00:25:48,818 --> 00:25:49,578
Look at this.

503
00:25:50,058 --> 00:25:51,738
Getting up so early to work.

504
00:25:51,738 --> 00:25:52,659
Of course, I'm poor.

505
00:25:52,818 --> 00:25:54,778
Who knows which nuisance it was?

506
00:25:55,139 --> 00:25:57,338
Had to schedule the departure for 9 AM.

507
00:25:57,619 --> 00:25:59,018
It made me stay up all night.

508
00:25:59,498 --> 00:26:02,778
It's said the road to Garden Hotel is
under repair. They told us to go early.

509
00:26:03,578 --> 00:26:04,379
Bad traffic, huh?

510
00:26:04,498 --> 00:26:04,998
Yeah.

511
00:26:08,219 --> 00:26:10,258
Did you hear about
Xu jumping ship to Wilson?

512
00:26:11,818 --> 00:26:12,939
He pulled a slick move.

513
00:26:13,379 --> 00:26:16,459
Having worked at GST for 26 years,

514
00:26:17,219 --> 00:26:19,058
he now turns traitor

515
00:26:19,738 --> 00:26:20,899
and has turned to the enemy.

516
00:26:23,258 --> 00:26:24,258
I also heard

517
00:26:24,818 --> 00:26:27,058
he plans to take Zhao Mei with him.

518
00:26:27,139 --> 00:26:28,219
That's not possible.

519
00:26:28,219 --> 00:26:29,778
How is it not possible?

520
00:26:30,018 --> 00:26:31,058
If Wilson

521
00:26:31,498 --> 00:26:34,179
gave Xu the title of Sales VP,

522
00:26:34,298 --> 00:26:37,179
then Zhao Mei would definitely
get a director position over there.

523
00:26:37,778 --> 00:26:39,578
Wilson's making a smart move.

524
00:26:40,058 --> 00:26:41,738
A Sales Director

525
00:26:41,899 --> 00:26:43,699
and a head of promotions.

526
00:26:44,179 --> 00:26:46,179
It's a perfect match.

527
00:26:46,179 --> 00:26:46,979
A perfect match?

528
00:26:46,979 --> 00:26:48,778
Boss, can we go now?

529
00:26:50,258 --> 00:26:51,058
I got up so early.

530
00:26:51,058 --> 00:26:51,939
Of course, I'll go.

531
00:26:53,578 --> 00:26:54,379
Let's go.

532
00:26:56,338 --> 00:26:56,939
I'm so sleepy.

533
00:27:01,018 --> 00:27:03,379
Mr. Dong, maybe you could take that car?

534
00:27:03,578 --> 00:27:04,379
That car has space.

535
00:27:04,738 --> 00:27:06,098
Why can't I ride in the first one?

536
00:27:08,659 --> 00:27:09,538
Fine, let's go.

537
00:27:12,778 --> 00:27:13,278
Peter.

538
00:27:13,738 --> 00:27:16,818
Earlier at the management meeting,
Barry clearly stated

539
00:27:16,939 --> 00:27:19,179
he wants the new Sales Director
to be a woman.

540
00:27:20,538 --> 00:27:22,179
So he wants to promote Zhao Mei?

541
00:27:22,538 --> 00:27:23,038
Yes.

542
00:27:23,379 --> 00:27:25,298
It's not the final decision yet,

543
00:27:25,699 --> 00:27:27,699
but we must find a way to stop it.

544
00:27:28,258 --> 00:27:29,018
Okay, I got it.

545
00:27:48,979 --> 00:27:49,859
I heard

546
00:27:52,818 --> 00:27:56,338
Mr. Xu wants to take you
with him to Wilson.

547
00:27:57,699 --> 00:27:58,578
How is that possible?

548
00:27:59,699 --> 00:28:01,379
If it were true, he'd take me long ago,

549
00:28:01,379 --> 00:28:02,498
and would not wait until now.

550
00:28:02,498 --> 00:28:03,778
Terms weren't agreed upon.

551
00:28:03,778 --> 00:28:04,738
Now they are.

552
00:28:04,738 --> 00:28:06,498
There were never any talks.

553
00:28:10,258 --> 00:28:11,578
It's all rumors.

554
00:28:15,619 --> 00:28:16,778
But I really want to know

555
00:28:16,778 --> 00:28:18,939
who exactly started these rumors.

556
00:28:18,939 --> 00:28:20,258
What? Got a suspect in mind?

557
00:28:20,778 --> 00:28:22,498
Yeah, I think
you're the most suspicious.

558
00:28:23,219 --> 00:28:24,179
So blunt?

559
00:28:25,859 --> 00:28:27,778
Actually,
I didn't spread rumors about you.

560
00:28:28,098 --> 00:28:29,098
But you're interesting.

561
00:28:29,298 --> 00:28:32,219
Most would keep it bottled up,
guessing and speculating.

562
00:28:32,778 --> 00:28:33,859
They wouldn't be as blunt.

563
00:28:35,298 --> 00:28:36,139
Of course.

564
00:28:36,498 --> 00:28:38,338
If I keep it inside and don't say it,

565
00:28:38,338 --> 00:28:40,139
this problem will always be my problem.

566
00:28:40,738 --> 00:28:41,538
If I say it out,

567
00:28:41,738 --> 00:28:43,538
whether the other person
admits it or not,

568
00:28:44,058 --> 00:28:46,139
I've kicked the ball over to their side.

569
00:28:46,498 --> 00:28:47,058
I see.

570
00:28:47,979 --> 00:28:48,578
You doubt me.

571
00:28:49,619 --> 00:28:50,298
Obviously.

572
00:28:58,179 --> 00:28:58,888
You are sleepy.

573
00:29:02,058 --> 00:29:03,179
You can take a nap.

574
00:29:03,778 --> 00:29:04,778
It'll take two hours.

575
00:29:06,018 --> 00:29:06,538
Okay.

576
00:29:12,399 --> 00:29:13,979
Sir, please turn the AC up a bit.

577
00:29:23,202 --> 00:29:26,088
(Nansha Garden Hotel)

578
00:29:30,850 --> 00:29:32,834
(Gustav Sapet China, Garden Hotel)

579
00:29:36,802 --> 00:29:39,624
(Gennadiy Night Private Dinner)

580
00:29:40,699 --> 00:29:41,258
Mr. Tang.

581
00:29:41,738 --> 00:29:42,238
Welcome.

582
00:29:42,538 --> 00:29:43,139
Hello.

583
00:29:43,139 --> 00:29:43,899
Your room key.

584
00:29:44,538 --> 00:29:45,038
Mao.

585
00:29:46,498 --> 00:29:46,998
Boss.

586
00:29:47,058 --> 00:29:49,699
- Great waitresses. Where are they from?
- The event company.

587
00:29:49,699 --> 00:29:51,018
All carefully selected.

588
00:29:51,018 --> 00:29:51,818
Yu Wei'e.

589
00:29:52,578 --> 00:29:53,379
Promising.

590
00:29:53,939 --> 00:29:54,439
Mr. Tang.

591
00:29:54,738 --> 00:29:55,238
Boss.

592
00:29:55,459 --> 00:29:56,179
I'll carry my bag.

593
00:29:56,899 --> 00:29:58,098
Why put the banner there?

594
00:29:59,298 --> 00:30:00,818
Moving it right away, boss.

595
00:30:00,818 --> 00:30:01,899
Carefully selected?

596
00:30:02,419 --> 00:30:04,939
I called earlier, but you didn't answer.
Stuck in traffic?

597
00:30:05,058 --> 00:30:06,139
I noticed the one-hour trip

598
00:30:06,139 --> 00:30:06,738
took you two.

599
00:30:07,379 --> 00:30:08,098
A bit jammed.

600
00:30:08,298 --> 00:30:09,338
Boss, your room key.

601
00:30:12,058 --> 00:30:14,258
Why don't you go to your room
and rest for a bit?

602
00:30:14,498 --> 00:30:16,018
I'll take another look at the venue.

603
00:30:18,179 --> 00:30:18,679
Alright.

604
00:30:19,699 --> 00:30:21,619
I'll meet you at the venue
in half an hour.

605
00:30:23,818 --> 00:30:24,379
Thanks.

606
00:30:24,578 --> 00:30:25,139
This way.

607
00:30:37,139 --> 00:30:37,639
Which floor?

608
00:30:39,258 --> 00:30:39,778
Fifth floor.

609
00:30:41,098 --> 00:30:41,598
Room number?

610
00:30:41,979 --> 00:30:42,538
557.

611
00:30:44,098 --> 00:30:45,448
I'm in Room 558, right next door.

612
00:31:08,219 --> 00:31:09,058
Nice place.

613
00:31:10,859 --> 00:31:13,098
The waitresses' outfits are improper.
Too seductive.

614
00:31:14,498 --> 00:31:16,179
Understood. I'll have them get changed.

615
00:31:16,778 --> 00:31:17,899
Just replace the people.

616
00:31:18,619 --> 00:31:20,584
Tell the event company
to replace them with men.

617
00:31:21,219 --> 00:31:24,098
Men? Why change to men?

618
00:31:24,778 --> 00:31:27,459
The VIP clients are almost all men.

619
00:31:27,459 --> 00:31:28,379
There are few women.

620
00:31:28,379 --> 00:31:29,818
That's exactly why the change.

621
00:31:32,058 --> 00:31:34,098
Is it because of Xu's incident?

622
00:31:35,139 --> 00:31:37,659
Isn't that thing over?
And he's stepped down.

623
00:31:38,298 --> 00:31:39,778
Work is work.

624
00:31:39,859 --> 00:31:42,778
Having waitresses doesn't mean
sexual harassment will happen.

625
00:31:43,219 --> 00:31:45,058
Aren't you overthinking this?

626
00:31:45,538 --> 00:31:47,939
I'm not overthinking.
Xu's issue isn't over yet.

627
00:31:49,098 --> 00:31:50,699
Alright, I'll go tell them.

628
00:31:55,219 --> 00:31:55,719
Boss,

629
00:31:56,659 --> 00:31:58,578
I heard some news.

630
00:31:59,219 --> 00:32:00,619
Please don't be mad at me.

631
00:32:00,619 --> 00:32:01,139
Go ahead.

632
00:32:03,619 --> 00:32:04,578
I heard

633
00:32:04,778 --> 00:32:07,979
the big bosses want Zhao Mei
to be the Sales Director

634
00:32:07,979 --> 00:32:09,018
because she's a woman?

635
00:32:10,258 --> 00:32:10,888
It's possible.

636
00:32:11,379 --> 00:32:12,939
Wasn't it agreed it would be you?

637
00:32:13,459 --> 00:32:14,419
Who did you agree with?

638
00:32:14,979 --> 00:32:15,778
In the company,

639
00:32:16,298 --> 00:32:19,098
no one is more suitable than you
to take over from Mr. Xu.

640
00:32:19,098 --> 00:32:21,538
Making her Sales Director?
That's a joke.

641
00:32:21,538 --> 00:32:22,258
Keep it down.

642
00:32:24,778 --> 00:32:27,258
Zhao Mei hasn't even worked in sales.

643
00:32:27,258 --> 00:32:29,419
How can she be Sales Director?
What qualifies her?

644
00:32:29,778 --> 00:32:32,139
Our company
doesn't have many female executives.

645
00:32:32,459 --> 00:32:33,018
Who says?

646
00:32:33,298 --> 00:32:34,219
What about Qi Youlan?

647
00:32:34,219 --> 00:32:36,738
Qi Youlan is in HR.
Not business departments.

648
00:32:37,058 --> 00:32:38,979
That just proves the point.

649
00:32:39,298 --> 00:32:41,778
Women aren't suited to be executives
in business departments.

650
00:32:42,018 --> 00:32:45,338
Remember, respecting women
is our bottom line.

651
00:32:46,058 --> 00:32:48,498
I respect them. I respect women a lot.

652
00:32:48,498 --> 00:32:50,459
I have the utmost respect for women.

653
00:32:50,738 --> 00:32:52,738
I don't see them as weak.

654
00:32:52,738 --> 00:32:54,338
I see them as equal competitors.

655
00:32:54,619 --> 00:32:56,098
So you should have a fair fight,

656
00:32:56,098 --> 00:32:57,258
no holding back.

657
00:32:57,419 --> 00:32:58,738
And I hope the big bosses

658
00:32:58,738 --> 00:33:01,578
do not have a female executive
just for the sake of having one.

659
00:33:19,098 --> 00:33:21,778
I found Wilson's products
in the minibar.

660
00:33:21,778 --> 00:33:23,058
You should check too.

661
00:33:23,538 --> 00:33:25,798
Okay, got it. Thanks.

662
00:33:31,578 --> 00:33:33,738
A slip-up.
I'll go oversee it right away.

663
00:33:33,738 --> 00:33:34,459
And personally.

664
00:33:34,459 --> 00:33:36,058
The word "Wilson" won't appear.

665
00:33:36,058 --> 00:33:36,939
Enough talk. Hurry up.

666
00:34:05,578 --> 00:34:07,018
Since when do you like video calls?

667
00:34:07,498 --> 00:34:08,459
I'm meeting someone.

668
00:34:08,459 --> 00:34:10,618
The atmosphere here is great.
I wanted you to see it.

669
00:34:10,819 --> 00:34:11,819
Here, look.

670
00:34:12,618 --> 00:34:13,538
There's even a plane.

671
00:34:14,299 --> 00:34:15,176
It looks pretty nice.

672
00:34:15,739 --> 00:34:17,939
I'll reserve a table.
Let's dine here tonight.

673
00:34:19,058 --> 00:34:20,259
I'm not downtown.

674
00:34:20,979 --> 00:34:21,578
Where are you?

675
00:34:22,698 --> 00:34:24,098
The Nansha Garden Hotel.

676
00:34:24,538 --> 00:34:27,779
There's a VIP dinner tonight.
I won't be back until tomorrow.

677
00:34:29,058 --> 00:34:30,299
Why didn't you tell me?

678
00:34:33,058 --> 00:34:35,178
I told you. You must've forgotten.

679
00:34:36,498 --> 00:34:38,218
Alright, go ahead. We can talk later.

680
00:34:38,779 --> 00:34:39,299
Bye.

681
00:34:56,058 --> 00:34:57,339
It's so beautiful here.

682
00:34:59,379 --> 00:35:02,058
By the way, Mr. Li, the other party
will be here in five minutes.

683
00:35:08,218 --> 00:35:10,698
Mr. Li, today is my birthday.

684
00:35:11,859 --> 00:35:12,459
Really?

685
00:35:13,658 --> 00:35:14,379
Happy Birthday.

686
00:35:14,779 --> 00:35:15,279
Thank you.

687
00:35:15,939 --> 00:35:17,032
Let me treat you to dinner.

688
00:35:17,779 --> 00:35:19,538
I wonder if you're free tonight.

689
00:35:20,299 --> 00:35:21,058
Just the two of us?

690
00:35:25,058 --> 00:35:26,779
I have another appointment
after this ends.

691
00:35:27,058 --> 00:35:28,218
Not sure when it will finish.

692
00:35:30,058 --> 00:35:32,098
Then I'll book a table first.
I'll wait for you.

693
00:35:35,859 --> 00:35:36,538
This sign.

694
00:35:36,899 --> 00:35:37,859
(Gennadiy Night)
If there's a problem, it's on you.

695
00:35:43,739 --> 00:35:44,939
What a great figure.

696
00:35:46,538 --> 00:35:48,058
Nightclub promoters are different.

697
00:35:49,098 --> 00:35:50,859
Too bad she's in the wrong outfit today.

698
00:35:51,178 --> 00:35:53,578
It would be better
if she wore the uniform.

699
00:35:53,698 --> 00:35:54,819
What are you thinking?

700
00:35:54,819 --> 00:35:55,658
To have her

701
00:35:55,658 --> 00:35:56,859
toast the VIP clients tonight?

702
00:35:57,459 --> 00:35:59,259
But that's not a bad idea.

703
00:35:59,538 --> 00:36:02,459
We can replace all the waitresses
with female promoters.

704
00:36:05,498 --> 00:36:06,018
What's this?

705
00:36:06,819 --> 00:36:07,819
A voice recorder.

706
00:36:15,939 --> 00:36:17,138
Why did you bring her?

707
00:36:17,739 --> 00:36:18,538
I did it on purpose.

708
00:36:18,538 --> 00:36:19,038
Why?

709
00:36:19,618 --> 00:36:20,498
Lately, many people

710
00:36:20,498 --> 00:36:22,098
are gossiping
about you and Mr. Xu again.

711
00:36:22,098 --> 00:36:22,739
Who's saying it?

712
00:36:24,138 --> 00:36:26,538
Sales, suppliers, clients, and so on.

713
00:36:27,058 --> 00:36:28,218
They have a few chat groups.

714
00:36:28,218 --> 00:36:30,098
What does Zeng Zixuan
have to do with this?

715
00:36:31,138 --> 00:36:33,379
I was worried they'd use it against you.

716
00:36:33,578 --> 00:36:35,819
You know these people
start blabbering when they drink.

717
00:36:36,379 --> 00:36:37,339
With Zeng Zixuan here,

718
00:36:37,578 --> 00:36:39,178
they'll be embarrassed
to mention Mr. Xu.

719
00:36:39,618 --> 00:36:41,299
After all, Mr. Xu left because of her.

720
00:36:44,538 --> 00:36:47,459
Mr. Xu didn't leave
because of Zeng Zixuan.

721
00:36:47,859 --> 00:36:50,899
Mr. Xu left
because he made mistakes himself.

722
00:36:51,859 --> 00:36:52,859
Stop using her like this.

723
00:36:54,379 --> 00:36:56,578
Boss, I heard from the higher-ups

724
00:36:57,138 --> 00:36:59,368
you've been officially nominated
as the Sales Director.

725
00:37:01,192 --> 00:37:02,259
It's just a nomination.

726
00:37:02,538 --> 00:37:03,578
Yeah, just a nomination.

727
00:37:03,578 --> 00:37:04,618
You have no idea

728
00:37:04,939 --> 00:37:06,578
how bad the gossip will be.

729
00:37:07,379 --> 00:37:09,178
I was worried
they might hurt your reputation.

730
00:37:09,379 --> 00:37:10,498
Let them say what they want.

731
00:37:12,058 --> 00:37:13,658
Since I'm taking over Mr. Xu's role,

732
00:37:13,658 --> 00:37:15,538
I must have the nerve
to face what he faced.

733
00:37:15,538 --> 00:37:16,138
What's to fear?

734
00:37:16,618 --> 00:37:17,178
Boss,

735
00:37:17,578 --> 00:37:19,498
I volunteered to come.

736
00:37:19,498 --> 00:37:20,939
I don't care anymore.

737
00:37:20,939 --> 00:37:22,618
I want to do more for our department.

738
00:37:22,618 --> 00:37:23,339
Stop it.

739
00:37:24,018 --> 00:37:25,218
Whether you want to or not,

740
00:37:25,498 --> 00:37:27,058
don't show up tonight.

741
00:37:27,259 --> 00:37:29,498
Stay in my room, and don't go anywhere.

742
00:37:30,339 --> 00:37:31,538
Wang Hao, take her.

743
00:37:33,018 --> 00:37:33,518
Let's go.

744
00:37:41,859 --> 00:37:43,218
Why were the waitresses replaced?

745
00:37:45,018 --> 00:37:45,819
To avoid trouble?

746
00:37:46,739 --> 00:37:49,178
Right. They are all VIP guests today.

747
00:37:49,538 --> 00:37:50,739
Hard to control if they drink.

748
00:37:51,018 --> 00:37:52,018
Waiters are safer.

749
00:37:53,259 --> 00:37:54,339
By the way, I've heard

750
00:37:55,058 --> 00:37:56,419
Shen Mo's not coming.

751
00:37:57,058 --> 00:37:57,819
Family matters.

752
00:37:58,058 --> 00:37:59,339
Drive the car to the front door.

753
00:38:00,218 --> 00:38:00,779
Yes.

754
00:38:01,379 --> 00:38:03,538
Tell me when you arrive.
I'll meet you outside.

755
00:38:03,658 --> 00:38:05,058
You don't know anything.

756
00:38:05,058 --> 00:38:06,218
It's called being safe.

757
00:38:07,018 --> 00:38:08,018
Then she's not safe?

758
00:38:08,498 --> 00:38:10,658
Thousands of peach blossoms,
with just one acre left.

759
00:38:11,899 --> 00:38:13,979
Yu Wei'e is right.
You don't know anything.

760
00:38:19,739 --> 00:38:20,419
Mr. Peter.

761
00:38:20,419 --> 00:38:22,218
I just spoke with Shen Mo on the phone.

762
00:38:22,218 --> 00:38:25,218
He said he's on his way
to Nansha Garden Hotel.

763
00:38:25,339 --> 00:38:27,299
Really? That's great.

764
00:38:28,018 --> 00:38:29,459
Yes, and Jin Linsheng too.

765
00:38:29,618 --> 00:38:32,138
They're both coming in one car.
I'll leave them to you.

766
00:38:32,819 --> 00:38:33,739
Them both?

767
00:38:33,979 --> 00:38:34,479
Yes.

768
00:38:34,538 --> 00:38:36,218
Okay. I will take good care of them.

769
00:38:36,379 --> 00:38:37,339
Great, see you in a bit.

770
00:38:37,538 --> 00:38:38,459
Okay, see you.

771
00:38:45,859 --> 00:38:46,359
Mr. Fu.

772
00:38:46,658 --> 00:38:47,259
Mr. Dong.

773
00:38:47,259 --> 00:38:48,538
Long time no see.

774
00:38:55,158 --> 00:38:55,658
Ms. Su.

775
00:38:55,658 --> 00:38:57,018
Hello, Mr. Dong.

776
00:38:57,259 --> 00:38:58,698
- You're here.
- Congratulations.

777
00:38:58,698 --> 00:39:00,218
Yes, I'm here to congratulate you.

778
00:39:00,218 --> 00:39:00,739
Thank you.

779
00:39:00,739 --> 00:39:02,138
It's such a wonderful day.

780
00:39:02,138 --> 00:39:04,419
I felt I'd neglected my duty
when you left the car.

781
00:39:04,419 --> 00:39:05,608
There should be a red carpet.

782
00:39:06,259 --> 00:39:07,178
You're gorgeous today.

783
00:39:07,939 --> 00:39:09,939
The place you chose is really nice.

784
00:39:10,018 --> 00:39:10,859
It's nice, huh?

785
00:39:10,859 --> 00:39:11,618
It's very nice.

786
00:39:12,459 --> 00:39:13,178
This place...

787
00:39:22,578 --> 00:39:23,419
Mr. Shen.

788
00:39:23,979 --> 00:39:24,698
Hello, Mr. Shen.

789
00:39:25,058 --> 00:39:26,058
Mr. Jin.

790
00:39:26,498 --> 00:39:26,998
Hello.

791
00:39:27,299 --> 00:39:29,498
Take the luggage up to Room 823.

792
00:39:29,658 --> 00:39:30,158
Okay.

793
00:39:30,419 --> 00:39:30,979
See you later.

794
00:39:30,979 --> 00:39:31,939
Mr. Shen, come with me.

795
00:39:31,939 --> 00:39:32,839
- Mr. Jin.
- Okay.

796
00:39:34,899 --> 00:39:36,498
The rooms have been arranged

797
00:39:36,739 --> 00:39:38,259
with your specified orientation.

798
00:39:38,618 --> 00:39:39,658
The hotel breakfast

799
00:39:39,658 --> 00:39:42,819
is served from 7 AM to 10 AM.

800
00:39:42,819 --> 00:39:44,339
The gym is open 24 hours.

801
00:39:46,459 --> 00:39:47,058
You're welcome.

802
00:39:47,098 --> 00:39:48,178
If I need anything...

803
00:39:48,859 --> 00:39:49,359
Sure.

804
00:39:51,739 --> 00:39:52,819
Yes, put it here.

805
00:39:55,819 --> 00:39:57,138
Let us know if you need anything.

806
00:39:57,138 --> 00:39:57,939
Okay, thank you.

807
00:40:07,259 --> 00:40:08,658
Didn't you say you weren't coming?

808
00:40:08,739 --> 00:40:09,859
What changed your mind?

809
00:40:10,658 --> 00:40:11,538
I did have plans.

810
00:40:11,979 --> 00:40:12,779
But then I thought

811
00:40:14,098 --> 00:40:16,739
I should come. After all,
I owe you for your mom's cooking.

812
00:40:19,018 --> 00:40:20,058
You found out?

813
00:40:21,939 --> 00:40:24,058
Sorry, I didn't mean
to hide it from you.

814
00:40:24,058 --> 00:40:24,658
I understand.

815
00:40:28,058 --> 00:40:29,178
Thank you for helping me.

816
00:40:29,859 --> 00:40:31,138
I'm always willing to help you.

817
00:40:32,098 --> 00:40:33,618
I didn't agree to your request earlier

818
00:40:34,218 --> 00:40:36,498
because I turned down Peter first

819
00:40:37,339 --> 00:40:38,299
and then Dong Yue.

820
00:40:38,899 --> 00:40:42,618
If it ended up being you
who submitted Jin's and my names,

821
00:40:43,138 --> 00:40:43,979
it'd be bad for you.

822
00:40:45,218 --> 00:40:47,739
Not that they'd deliberately
make things hard for you,

823
